(12, 2, 'Whirlpool 7.5 kg  5 Star Inverter Fully-Automatic Top Loading Washing Machine with In-Built Heater ', 'Whirlpool ', 'Premium Edge to Edge aesthetic with 12 Wash Programs - Daily, Heavy, Delicates, Whites, Stainwash, Anti Bacterial, Eco, Woollens, Bed Sheet, Rinse + Spin, Spin, Wash Only. \r\nIn-Built Heater Technology: Can heat water at 3 different levels - Warm, Hot & Allergen free. \r\nIntellisense Inverter Motor: consumes less energy and produces less noise and vibration. \r\n360 Bloomwash Action with Hexabloom Impeller. \r\nHard Water Wash Technology. \r\nLED Digital Display & Soft Close Lid: gives a premium experience and protects the glass lid from any damage. \r\nAuto Tub Clean Feature.', '645a02d19e541.jpg', '230.00', 'washing machine'),
